layout.p:
Columns: 2;
                                                  ruled lines: 24;
                                                  written lines: 24; Uniform layout. Visible pricking in outer margins and complete hard-point ruling. Imperfect at the end. Hair side and flesh side of folios distinguishable. The last word of a folio usually repeated at the beginning of the next. Initial verses written occasionally in red ink. Gilt edges.
